#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kpat.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"KPat (aka KPatience) is a relaxing card sorting game. To win the game a "
"player has to arrange a single deck of cards in certain order amongst each "
"other."
msgstr ""
"KPat (tamén chamado KPatience) é un xogo relaxante que consiste en ordenar "
"cartas. Para gañar hai que ordenar un mazo de cartas dun xeito concreto."

